@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### List All Guides (no filters)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/guides HTTP/1.1

### List All Guides with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/guides?page=1&limit=5 HTTP/1.1

### List Active Guides Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/guides?is_active=true HTTP/1.1

### List Inactive Guides Only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/guides?is_active=false HTTP/1.1

### Filter Guides by Single Specialty
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/guides?specialties=diving HTTP/1.1

### Filter Guides by Multiple Specialties (comma-separated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/guides?specialties=diving,hiking HTTP/1.1

### Filter Active Guides with Specialty
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/guides?is_active=true&specialties=safari HTTP/1.1

### Combined Filters with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/guides?page=1&limit=10&is_active=true&specialties=climbing HTTP/1.1

### Get Guide by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/guides/guide123 HTTP/1.1

### Get Guide Availability (Replace dates and guide ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/guides/guide123/availability?startDate=2026-02-01&endDate=2026-02-28 HTTP/1.1

### Get Guide Availability (7 days from today)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/guides/guide123/availability?startDate=2026-01-20&endDate=2026-01-27 HTTP/1.1

### Get Guide Reviews
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/guides/guide123/reviews HTTP/1.1

### Get Guide Reviews with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/guides/guide123/reviews?page=1&limit=5 HTTP/1.1

